1
00:01:43,162 --> 00:01:44,795
- INUYASHA DEFEATED GOSHINKI,

2
00:01:44,828 --> 00:01:47,162
THE DEMON CREATED
FROM NARAKU'S BODY.

3
00:01:47,195 --> 00:01:51,162
KAIJINBO USED ITS FANGS TO FORGE
THE EVIL SWORD TOKIJIN,

4
00:01:51,195 --> 00:01:53,862
WHICH HE THEN WIELDED
AGAINST INUYASHA.

5
00:01:53,895 --> 00:01:56,195
HIS STRANGE EYES
AND ACTIONS CONVINCED US

6
00:01:56,228 --> 00:01:59,828
THAT HE WAS POSSESSED
BY THE WICKED SWORD.

7
00:01:59,862 --> 00:02:01,162
- PLAYTIME IS OVER.

8
00:02:01,195 --> 00:02:06,328
- YOU SHOULD HAVE KILLED ME
WHILE YOU HAD THE CHANCE...

9
00:02:06,362 --> 00:02:08,695
BEFORE I BECAME A DEMON AGAIN.

10
00:02:08,728 --> 00:02:12,195
- I'LL SLICE YOU
IN HALF, INUYASHA!

11
00:02:12,228 --> 00:02:12,962
ARRGH!

12
00:02:12,995 --> 00:02:14,795
- DAMN THAT OLD MAN!

13
00:02:14,828 --> 00:02:16,662
ARRGH!

14
00:02:16,695 --> 00:02:18,628
[GASPS]

15
00:02:27,162 --> 00:02:29,595
[GROWLING]

16
00:02:32,828 --> 00:02:34,328
- IT'S A DRAW!

17
00:02:34,362 --> 00:02:36,728
[SHIPPO GRUNTS]

18
00:02:38,528 --> 00:02:40,828
[GRUNTING]

19
00:02:43,495 --> 00:02:45,762
- I'M NOT GOING
TO STAND FOR ANY DRAW.

20
00:02:45,795 --> 00:02:47,162
THE TOKIJIN IS STRONG ALL RIGHT,

21
00:02:47,195 --> 00:02:49,595
BUT KAIJINBO DOESN'T
KNOW HOW TO HANDLE IT.

22
00:02:49,628 --> 00:02:53,895
I COULD HAVE DONE HIM
IN ALREADY IF TETSUSAIGA
DIDN'T WEIGH SO MUCH.

23
00:02:53,928 --> 00:02:56,362
WHAT THE HELL WAS
TOTOSAI THINKING,

24
00:02:56,395 --> 00:02:59,595
MAKING IT SO BLOODY HEAVY?

25
00:02:59,628 --> 00:03:00,762
- PATHETIC!

26
00:03:00,795 --> 00:03:03,795
YOU DON'T EVEN HAVE THE STRENGTH
TO HOLD UP YOUR OWN SWORD!

27
00:03:03,828 --> 00:03:05,262
- DAMN IT!

28
00:03:05,295 --> 00:03:06,662
- PREPARE YOURSELF!

29
00:03:06,695 --> 00:03:08,828
THIS TIME,
YOU'LL MEET YOUR MAKER!

30
00:03:08,862 --> 00:03:11,062
- NOT IF I CAN HELP IT!

31
00:03:11,095 --> 00:03:12,462
ARRGH!

32
00:03:12,495 --> 00:03:15,028
[GRUNTING]

33
00:03:21,995 --> 00:03:22,795
[LAUGHS]

34
00:03:22,828 --> 00:03:23,695
- PATHETIC, TOTOSAI!

35
00:03:23,728 --> 00:03:27,928
I WOULD HAVE EXPECTED
MUCH BETTER FROM--

36
00:03:31,728 --> 00:03:33,262
[GASPING]

37
00:03:43,562 --> 00:03:44,995
- INCREDIBLE!
- YES.

38
00:03:45,028 --> 00:03:50,362
THE SWORD HELD UP, BUT
KAIJINBO HIMSELF WAS UNABLE
TO WITHSTAND ITS POWER.

39
00:03:50,395 --> 00:03:53,562
THE VERY SWORD HE FORGED
OVERPOWERED HIM.

40
00:03:53,595 --> 00:03:55,628
THE WRETCHED FOOL DESERVED IT.

41
00:03:55,662 --> 00:03:58,028
[PANTING]

42
00:04:01,862 --> 00:04:03,828
[GROWLS]

43
00:04:04,428 --> 00:04:07,195
- TOTOSAI,
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU!

44
00:04:07,228 --> 00:04:09,095
- SOMETHING ABOUT THE SWORD
YOU DON'T CARE FOR?

45
00:04:09,128 --> 00:04:13,562
- HOW IN THE HELL
DO YOU FIGURE I CAN CARRY
AROUND SUCH A HEAVY SWORD?

46
00:04:13,595 --> 00:04:15,395
ONE THRUST AND I NEED
TO STOP AND REST!

47
00:04:15,428 --> 00:04:19,828
- DO YOU WISH TO KNOW HOW TO
HANDLE THE HEAVY TETSUSAIGA?

48
00:04:19,862 --> 00:04:20,628
- HUH?

49
00:04:20,662 --> 00:04:22,995
- YOU MEAN,
THERE'S A WAY TO DO IT?

50
00:04:23,028 --> 00:04:24,495
- AND IT'S SIMPLE.

51
00:04:24,528 --> 00:04:26,028
- HMM.

52
00:04:26,062 --> 00:04:28,962
[WIND RUSTLING]

53
00:04:33,362 --> 00:04:35,062
- YOU AREN'T GOING TO TELL ME
THAT THE ANSWER

54
00:04:35,095 --> 00:04:37,295
IS IN BUILDING UP
MY OWN STRENGTH, ARE YOU?

55
00:04:37,328 --> 00:04:38,995
[GASPS]
- OH!

56
00:04:39,028 --> 00:04:39,995
- I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN!

57
00:04:40,028 --> 00:04:42,695
- THE OLD GUY SHOULDN'T
HAVE EVEN BROUGHT IT UP.

58
00:04:42,728 --> 00:04:44,495
- MM-HMM!

59
00:04:46,462 --> 00:04:49,295
- STRANGE THAT THE EVIL
AURA AROUND THE SWORD

60
00:04:49,328 --> 00:04:51,162
STILL HASN'T DISSIPATED.

61
00:04:51,195 --> 00:04:53,262
- INDEED.

62
00:04:53,695 --> 00:04:56,828
NO! THE EVIL WON'T
ALLOW ME TO EXTRACT IT!

63
00:04:56,862 --> 00:04:59,962
WHO COULD HAVE COMMISSIONED
KAIJINBO TO FORGE SUCH A SWORD?

64
00:04:59,995 --> 00:05:02,995
- WE'LL HAVE TO CONSTRUCT
A BARRIER AROUND TOKIJIN

65
00:05:03,028 --> 00:05:03,995
TO CONTAIN THE AURA.

66
00:05:04,028 --> 00:05:06,995
OTHERWISE, WE WON'T BE ABLE
TO CONTROL ITS EVIL.

67
00:05:07,028 --> 00:05:10,895
- MIROKU, CAN'T YOU PUT SOME
KIND OF SACRED SPELL ON IT?

68
00:05:10,928 --> 00:05:12,195
- THE AURA'S TOO STRONG.

69
00:05:12,228 --> 00:05:14,495
I'M NOT SURE ANY
OF MY SPELLS WOULD BE ABLE

70
00:05:14,528 --> 00:05:15,495
TO SEAL IT COMPLETELY.

71
00:05:15,528 --> 00:05:18,995
- WHAT ABOUT YOUR IDEA
TO CREATE A BARRIER, THEN?

72
00:05:19,028 --> 00:05:20,195
- EASIER SAID THAN DONE.

73
00:05:20,228 --> 00:05:23,828
WE'LL NEED TO HIRE MEN TO BUILD
IT, AND THAT REQUIRES MONEY,

74
00:05:23,862 --> 00:05:25,395
WHICH WE'RE SADLY LACKING.

75
00:05:25,428 --> 00:05:28,595
- THEN MAKE SOME MONEY WITH
YOUR FAKE FORTUNE-TELLING.

76
00:05:28,628 --> 00:05:31,195
- I MAKE AN HONEST LIVING,
I'LL HAVE YOU KNOW!

77
00:05:31,228 --> 00:05:34,895
- YOUR JOB AS A MONK IS TO HELP
PEOPLE, SO HOW ABOUT HELPING US?

78
00:05:34,928 --> 00:05:36,062
- POINT TAKEN.

79
00:05:36,095 --> 00:05:38,328
IF I DO AGREE TO THIS, I'LL NEED
TO KEEP SOME OF THE MONEY

80
00:05:38,362 --> 00:05:40,762
TO ENTERTAIN MYSELF
WITH THE LADIES.

81
00:05:40,795 --> 00:05:43,162
I MAY NOT MAKE
AS MUCH AS WE NEED.

82
00:05:43,195 --> 00:05:44,162
HMM.

83
00:05:44,195 --> 00:05:45,795
- COULDN'T YOU FORGET
THE LADIES JUST THIS ONCE?

84
00:05:45,828 --> 00:05:47,762
- I'VE HEARD MORE
THAN I NEED TO.

85
00:05:47,795 --> 00:05:49,062
WE'RE WASTING TIME HERE.

86
00:05:49,095 --> 00:05:52,328
I'LL USE TETSUSAIGA
TO SMASH IT TO BITS.

87
00:05:52,362 --> 00:05:54,395
[GRUNTS]

88
00:05:58,062 --> 00:05:59,328
WHAT?

89
00:05:59,362 --> 00:06:01,695
AAH! UGH!

90
00:06:04,228 --> 00:06:07,095
- IS TOKIJIN UNBREAKABLE?

91
00:06:10,428 --> 00:06:12,695
- ITS EVIL POWER
IS AWESOME.

92
00:06:12,728 --> 00:06:13,995
- ALMOST AS IF IT'S ALIVE.

93
00:06:14,028 --> 00:06:16,595
- WHO DO YOU THINK
ASKED KAIJINBO TO MAKE IT
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

94
00:06:16,628 --> 00:06:18,262
- WE CAN TALK ABOUT THAT
LATER, BUT RIGHT NOW,

95
00:06:18,295 --> 00:06:20,562
WE SHOULD DISTANCE
OURSELVES FROM IT.

96
00:06:20,595 --> 00:06:22,228
- MMM.
- YOU MEAN YOU WANT US TO RUN?

97
00:06:22,262 --> 00:06:25,328
ANYONE CAPABLE OF DRAWING
OUT A SWORD OF SUCH EVIL

98
00:06:25,362 --> 00:06:26,728
WOULD HAVE ENORMOUS POWER.

99
00:06:26,762 --> 00:06:28,628
YOU'RE NO MATCH AT PRESENT.

100
00:06:28,662 --> 00:06:30,428
- HMPH!

101
00:06:30,462 --> 00:06:31,828
I'M WAITING HERE.

102
00:06:31,862 --> 00:06:32,962
- INUYASHA.

103
00:06:32,995 --> 00:06:35,195
- BUT IF YOU STAY BY THE SWORD,
YOU MIGHT BE IN DANGER.

104
00:06:35,228 --> 00:06:38,695
- HE'S RIGHT.
IT'S WISER TO DISTANCE
YOURSELF FOR NOW.

105
00:06:38,728 --> 00:06:39,762
- NO.
DO WHAT YOU WANT,

106
00:06:39,795 --> 00:06:42,562
BUT I'M NOT GOING TO MOVE
A SINGLE MUSCLE.

107
00:06:42,595 --> 00:06:43,462
[SIGHS]

108
00:06:43,495 --> 00:06:44,862
- KAGOME, COME HERE A MOMENT.

109
00:06:44,895 --> 00:06:48,362
KNOWING INUYASHA'S CHARACTER,
HE REALLY ISN'T VERY LIKELY

110
00:06:48,395 --> 00:06:49,395
TO MOVE AWAY FROM THE SWORD.

111
00:06:49,428 --> 00:06:52,728
I SUGGEST WE STAY NEAR
AND KEEP WATCH OVER HIM.

112
00:06:52,762 --> 00:06:53,995
- OK.

113
00:06:54,028 --> 00:06:56,762
- WE'LL WAIT FOR ONE ENTIRE DAY,
WHEN HE'S CALMED DOWN SOMEWHAT.

114
00:06:56,795 --> 00:07:00,062
TOMORROW MORNING, IF HE STILL
INSISTS ON STAYING BY THE SWORD,

115
00:07:00,095 --> 00:07:04,095
THEN YOU CAN USE YOUR COMMAND ON
HIM, KAGOME, TO MAKE HIM SIT.

116
00:07:04,128 --> 00:07:05,862
I'LL THEN STEAL UP
FROM BEHIND HIM

117
00:07:05,895 --> 00:07:07,962
AND STRIKE HIM HARD
WITH MY STAFF,

118
00:07:07,995 --> 00:07:09,262
KNOCKING HIM UNCONSCIOUS.

119
00:07:09,295 --> 00:07:12,762
AND THAT'S WHEN WE WILL GATHER
HIM UP AND FLEE FROM THIS PLACE.

120
00:07:12,795 --> 00:07:14,828
- ISN'T THAT GOING
A LITTLE OVERBOARD?

121
00:07:14,862 --> 00:07:18,328
- PERHAPS, BUT DRASTIC TIMES
CALL FOR DRASTIC MEASURES.

122
00:07:18,362 --> 00:07:20,762
- ALL RIGHT.
LET'S DO IT THEN.

123
00:07:20,795 --> 00:07:21,928
- TILL TOMORROW MORNING.

124
00:07:21,962 --> 00:07:26,562
- I WONDER IF I SAID SOMETHING
THAT I SHOULDN'T HAVE SAID.

125
00:07:26,595 --> 00:07:29,162
[WIND RUSTLING]

126
00:07:29,195 --> 00:07:31,762
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

127
00:07:35,862 --> 00:07:37,762
- HMM.

128
00:07:43,795 --> 00:07:45,462
[FIRE CRACKLING]

129
00:07:45,495 --> 00:07:49,995
[SIGH]
- WHAT COULD BE TAKING
LORD SESSHOMARU SO LONG?

130
00:07:50,028 --> 00:07:50,995
[GASPS]

131
00:07:51,028 --> 00:07:52,162
- THAT FOOL KAIJINBO!

132
00:07:52,195 --> 00:07:56,328
WHERE IN THE WORLD COULD HE HAVE
GOTTEN TO WITH YOUR SWORD?

133
00:07:56,362 --> 00:07:58,462
- LORD SESSHOMARU!

134
00:07:58,495 --> 00:07:59,895
[LAUGHS]

135
00:07:59,928 --> 00:08:01,995
- STOP, RIN.
DO NOT MOVE.

136
00:08:02,028 --> 00:08:03,962
[GASPS]

137
00:08:03,995 --> 00:08:06,628
- HMM.

138
00:08:16,262 --> 00:08:17,495
- A WOMAN.

139
00:08:17,528 --> 00:08:18,495
- [SNIFFING]

140
00:08:18,528 --> 00:08:19,528
I KNOW THAT SCENT.

141
00:08:19,562 --> 00:08:22,195
SHE SMELLS MUCH LIKE
THE STRANGE BEAST THAT OFFERED

142
00:08:22,228 --> 00:08:24,062
TO LEND YOU
THE SEVERED HUMAN ARM.

143
00:08:24,095 --> 00:08:28,462
THE DEMON THAT DISGUISED HIMSELF
WITH A BABOON PALATE.

144
00:08:31,395 --> 00:08:35,028
HIS WRETCHED PLAN TOOK US
TO HELL AND BACK.

145
00:08:35,062 --> 00:08:36,028
CURSE HIM!

146
00:08:36,062 --> 00:08:38,495
YOUR ARM WAS ALMOST BURNED OFF!

147
00:08:38,528 --> 00:08:43,128
AND I WAS BEATEN
TO A PULP BY THAT MONK!

148
00:08:45,928 --> 00:08:49,128
OH, SIMPLY RECALLING
THAT INCIDENT MAKES ME ILL!

149
00:08:49,162 --> 00:08:50,395
- I RECALL THE SCENT.

150
00:08:50,428 --> 00:08:53,795
IT IS THE SAME AS THE BEAST
THAT ATTEMPTED TO TRAP ME,

151
00:08:53,828 --> 00:08:55,962
THE ONE WHO IS KNOWN AS NARAKU.

152
00:08:55,995 --> 00:09:00,428
- SO, YOU MUST BE INUYASHA'S
BROTHER SESSHOMARU.

153
00:09:00,462 --> 00:09:02,795
YOU'RE VERY CLEVER.

154
00:09:03,095 --> 00:09:06,595
I AM KAGURA,
THE WIND SORCERESS,

155
00:09:06,628 --> 00:09:08,828
AN INCARNATION OF NARAKU.

156
00:09:08,862 --> 00:09:10,062
- INCARNATION?

157
00:09:10,095 --> 00:09:11,395
- CORRECT.

158
00:09:11,428 --> 00:09:15,062
SESSHOMARU, THE FANGS YOU
DELIVERED TO KAIJINBO
TO MAKE YOUR SWORD

159
00:09:15,095 --> 00:09:17,162
WERE THOSE A DEMON
CALLED GOSHINKI.

160
00:09:17,195 --> 00:09:20,295
LIKE ME, HE WAS ALSO
CREATED FROM NARAKU.

161
00:09:20,328 --> 00:09:21,795
- ALL VERY INTERESTING,

162
00:09:21,828 --> 00:09:25,428
BUT DID YOU SEARCH ME OUT
TO SIMPLY TELL ME THIS?

163
00:09:25,462 --> 00:09:26,495
- HMM.

164
00:09:26,528 --> 00:09:28,295
- CAN YOU NOT DETECT ITS SCENT?

165
00:09:28,328 --> 00:09:30,762
TOKIJIN REEKS
OF GOSHINKI'S AURA.

166
00:09:30,795 --> 00:09:32,662
IT IS CLOSER THAN YOU THINK.

167
00:09:32,695 --> 00:09:35,528
[GUST OF WIND]

168
00:09:38,662 --> 00:09:41,995
YOU ARE THE SWORD'S
RIGHTFUL OWNER.

169
00:09:46,962 --> 00:09:49,628
- I AM NOT SORRY
TO SEE HER LEAVE SO SOON.

170
00:09:49,662 --> 00:09:53,528
I DON'T BELIEVE I'VE SEEN
SUCH AN ARROGANT WOMAN.

171
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:58,128
- RIN, YOU'RE FREE TO MOVE NOW.

172
00:09:58,162 --> 00:10:00,228
- YES, MY LORD!

173
00:10:00,262 --> 00:10:02,262
AHH!

174
00:10:04,295 --> 00:10:07,028
[RIN STRETCHES AND LAUGHS]
- THE TOKIJIN.

175
00:10:07,062 --> 00:10:09,262
- SPEAKING OF STRANGE WOMEN.

176
00:10:09,295 --> 00:10:12,128
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

177
00:10:18,162 --> 00:10:19,328
- WOULD YOU GET OFF MY BACK?

178
00:10:19,362 --> 00:10:22,562
STOP SAYING THE SAME
THING OVER AND OVER!

179
00:10:22,595 --> 00:10:24,628
- HMM?

180
00:10:26,828 --> 00:10:29,562
- I WILL NOT STOP
UNTIL I HAVE YOUR PROMISE!

181
00:10:29,595 --> 00:10:32,595
YOU MUST VOW NEVER
TO ABANDON TETSUSAIGA AGAIN!

182
00:10:32,628 --> 00:10:33,562
- HMPH!

183
00:10:33,595 --> 00:10:35,962
- SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD DO, KAGOME?

184
00:10:35,995 --> 00:10:37,662
- HUH?
- I'VE BEEN THINKING.

185
00:10:37,695 --> 00:10:42,528
PERHAPS I SHOULD COME RIGHT OUT
AND TELL INUYASHA THE TRUTH.

186
00:10:42,562 --> 00:10:44,262
- THE TRUTH.

187
00:10:44,295 --> 00:10:45,528
ABOUT HIS SWORD?

188
00:10:45,562 --> 00:10:49,628
THAT TETSUSAIGA KEEPS INUYASHA'S
DEMON ASPECT LOCKED INSIDE HIM?

189
00:10:49,662 --> 00:10:50,828
- YES.

190
00:10:50,862 --> 00:10:53,562
HE DOESN'T KNOW THAT, WHICH IS
WHY HE ABANDONS IT SOMETIMES.

191
00:10:53,595 --> 00:10:55,128
- MM-HMM.

192
00:10:56,262 --> 00:11:01,595
INUYASHA TRANSFORMED WHILE HE
WAS TRYING TO KILL GOSHINKI.

193
00:11:02,495 --> 00:11:06,895
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT AND WE SHOULD
TELL HIM ABOUT TETSUSAIGA.

194
00:11:08,295 --> 00:11:10,428
- YOU MUST NOT TELL HIM!

195
00:11:10,462 --> 00:11:11,528
- MYOGA, IT'S YOU.

196
00:11:11,562 --> 00:11:13,462
- YOU KNOW WHAT
MASTER INUYASHA IS LIKE.

197
00:11:13,495 --> 00:11:16,528
IF HE LEARNS THE SECRET,
HE'LL SURELY ABANDON THE SWORD

198
00:11:16,562 --> 00:11:21,128
AND COME TO RELY ON HIS
TRANSFORMED CLAWS AND FANGS.

199
00:11:21,162 --> 00:11:22,095
- YES.

200
00:11:22,128 --> 00:11:24,462
I SUPPOSE HE'LL
FIND THEM ADDICTIVE.

201
00:11:24,495 --> 00:11:25,562
- OF COURSE.

202
00:11:25,595 --> 00:11:28,695
AFTER ALL, INUYASHA IS
A SIMPLETON AT HEART, REMEMBER?

203
00:11:28,728 --> 00:11:31,495
- MM-HMM, WITHOUT A DOUBT.

204
00:11:31,528 --> 00:11:32,495
- HMM.

205
00:11:32,528 --> 00:11:34,428
- HUH?

206
00:11:35,428 --> 00:11:37,728
- YOU CERTAINLY
KEEP YOURSELF BUSY.

207
00:11:37,762 --> 00:11:41,995
CHANGING INTO A HUMAN ONE
MINUTE, A GOBLIN THE NEXT.

208
00:11:42,028 --> 00:11:44,762
- I'M A DEMON, NOT A GOBLIN.

209
00:11:45,695 --> 00:11:49,662
IT'S NOT EXACTLY LIKE I HAVE
ANY IDEA WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.

210
00:11:49,695 --> 00:11:51,628
- DON'T YOU KNOW
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

211
00:11:51,662 --> 00:11:53,428
YOU REALLY ARE DIMWITTED!

212
00:11:53,462 --> 00:11:54,862
- HMPH!

213
00:11:54,895 --> 00:11:56,228
- TOTOSAI!

214
00:11:56,262 --> 00:11:57,862
- WHAT'S HE GOING TO SAY?

215
00:11:57,895 --> 00:11:58,995
- NOT THE SECRET!

216
00:11:59,028 --> 00:12:02,328
- MYOGA TOLD ME THAT
YOU TRANSFORM INTO A FULL DEMON

217
00:12:02,362 --> 00:12:04,028
WHEN YOU'RE ON
THE VERGE OF DYING.

218
00:12:04,062 --> 00:12:06,295
THAT'S NOT TOO
SURPRISING, REALLY,

219
00:12:06,328 --> 00:12:07,995
SEEING AS YOU ARE A HALF-DEMON.

220
00:12:08,028 --> 00:12:12,262
BUT IF YOU ASK ME,
YOUR STRENGTH DOESN'T LIE
IN YOUR DEMON NATURE.

221
00:12:12,295 --> 00:12:16,362
AS I EXPLAINED TO YOU,
THE WEIGHT OF YOUR
REPAIRED TETSUSAIGA

222
00:12:16,395 --> 00:12:19,262
COMES FROM THE FANG
I USED TO FORGE IT.

223
00:12:19,295 --> 00:12:20,595
- HMM.

224
00:12:20,628 --> 00:12:25,662
- ORIGINALLY, TETSUSAIGA
WAS FORGED FROM YOUR
FATHER'S FANGS ALONE.

225
00:12:25,695 --> 00:12:30,662
IN OTHER WORDS, YOU ARE RELYING
ON YOUR FATHER TO PROTECT YOU.

226
00:12:30,695 --> 00:12:32,962
BUT NOW TETSUSAIGA
IS DIFFERENT.

227
00:12:32,995 --> 00:12:35,895
NOW YOU MUST MASTER
YOUR OWN FANG,

228
00:12:35,928 --> 00:12:38,462
AND YOU MUST PROTECT YOURSELF.

229
00:12:38,495 --> 00:12:40,295
[GASPS]

230
00:12:40,328 --> 00:12:43,728
ONCE YOU MANAGE TO FREELY
WIELD THIS NEW TETSUSAIGA,

231
00:12:43,762 --> 00:12:48,328
YOU WILL HAVE TRULY DISCOVERED
YOUR OWN STRENGTH.

232
00:12:48,362 --> 00:12:49,695
- HMM.

233
00:12:49,728 --> 00:12:50,828
[APPLAUSE]
HUH?

234
00:12:50,862 --> 00:12:53,028
- THAT'S RIGHT.
IT IS JUST AS YOU
HAVE SAID, TOTOSAI.

235
00:12:53,062 --> 00:12:55,962
- YEP, EXACTLY.
- YOU CAN DO IT, INUYASHA.

236
00:12:55,995 --> 00:12:57,328
YOU'VE GOT THE WILLPOWER.

237
00:12:57,362 --> 00:13:00,028
YOU CAN DO ANYTHING
YOU SET YOUR MIND TO.

238
00:13:00,062 --> 00:13:02,328
- YEAH, I GUESS SO.

239
00:13:02,362 --> 00:13:07,195
WHY DO I GET THIS FEELING
I'VE BEEN CONNED?

240
00:13:07,228 --> 00:13:08,962
[THUNDER]

241
00:13:10,928 --> 00:13:12,928
[WIND HOWLING]

242
00:13:20,795 --> 00:13:22,428
HMM?

243
00:13:31,862 --> 00:13:34,928
- [ROARING]

244
00:13:39,628 --> 00:13:41,428
- [GROANING]

245
00:13:47,295 --> 00:13:49,595
- [GASPING]
- SESSHOMARU.

246
00:13:49,628 --> 00:13:51,928
- AAH! OH, NO! NOT HIM!

247
00:13:51,962 --> 00:13:54,262
- WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

248
00:13:54,295 --> 00:13:56,162
- JUST WHAT I WOULD ASK YOU.

249
00:13:56,195 --> 00:13:57,962
I'VE MERELY COME FOR THIS SWORD.

250
00:13:57,995 --> 00:14:00,295
IT SEEMS THE DEMON
YOU KILLED WAS SO BITTER,

251
00:14:00,328 --> 00:14:02,795
IT DESIRED REVENGE
EVEN AFTER ITS REMAINS

252
00:14:02,828 --> 00:14:04,428
WERE FORGED INTO A SWORD.

253
00:14:04,462 --> 00:14:06,895
- WHAT?
- HOW DOES HE KNOW THAT TOKIJIN

254
00:14:06,928 --> 00:14:09,262
WAS CREATED FROM
GOSHINKI'S FANGS?

255
00:14:09,295 --> 00:14:10,462
- IT MUST MEAN THAT--

256
00:14:10,495 --> 00:14:15,262
- I WAS THE ONE WHO COMMISSIONED
KAIJINBO TO MAKE THIS SWORD.

257
00:14:15,295 --> 00:14:16,162
[GASPING]

258
00:14:16,195 --> 00:14:18,128
- SESSHOMARU,
YOU MUST NOT TOUCH TOKIJIN!

259
00:14:18,162 --> 00:14:21,695
EVEN YOU WILL BE POSSESSED
BY THE SWORD'S EVIL AURA.

260
00:14:21,728 --> 00:14:24,795
HEED MY WARNING,
I IMPLORE YOU!

261
00:14:36,228 --> 00:14:37,595
- PATHETIC FOOL.

262
00:14:37,628 --> 00:14:40,462
JUST WHO DO YOU TAKE ME FOR?

263
00:14:43,728 --> 00:14:46,395
- THE EVIL AURA!

264
00:14:47,695 --> 00:14:50,228
IT'S...DISSIPATING!

265
00:14:50,262 --> 00:14:54,028
- THE EVIL AURA WAS
OVERTAKEN BY SESSHOMARU.

266
00:14:54,062 --> 00:14:57,095
I DON'T CARE MUCH FOR HIM.

267
00:14:57,128 --> 00:15:01,128
- HMM. I SEE THE SWORD HAS
CHOSEN ME AS ITS MASTER.

268
00:15:01,162 --> 00:15:02,895
DRAW YOUR SWORD, INUYASHA.

269
00:15:02,928 --> 00:15:05,695
THERE'S SOMETHING
I WISH TO VERIFY.

270
00:15:05,728 --> 00:15:06,962
[WIND RUSTLING]

271
00:15:06,995 --> 00:15:08,795
- SOMETHING ABOUT ME?

272
00:15:08,828 --> 00:15:10,562
- DON'T DO IT, INUYASHA!

273
00:15:10,595 --> 00:15:11,695
- WOULD YOU LET GO OF ME?

274
00:15:11,728 --> 00:15:14,628
- DO YOU HONESTLY THINK
YOU CAN DEFEAT HIM?

275
00:15:14,662 --> 00:15:15,895
- HUH.

276
00:15:15,928 --> 00:15:18,495
I CAN'T EXACTLY TELL HIM TO COME
BACK WHEN I'M FINISHED TRAINING.

277
00:15:18,528 --> 00:15:19,562
- PRECISELY.

278
00:15:19,595 --> 00:15:21,962
COME AT ME, LITTLE BROTHER.

279
00:15:21,995 --> 00:15:23,328
I'LL MAKE IT EASY.

280
00:15:23,362 --> 00:15:25,762
I SHALL COME FOR YOU.

281
00:15:27,195 --> 00:15:31,062
- HUH. YOU'RE GOING
TO REGRET THIS, SESSHOMARU!

282
00:15:31,095 --> 00:15:34,162
OH, THIS THING IS WAY TOO HEAVY.

283
00:15:35,595 --> 00:15:37,795
[GRUNTS]

284
00:15:38,695 --> 00:15:40,395
AAH! AAH!

285
00:15:40,428 --> 00:15:43,062
- THE BEST HE CAN DO
IS BLOCK THE ATTACK.

286
00:15:43,095 --> 00:15:45,328
- HIS SWORD IS
TOO POWERFUL FOR HIM.

287
00:15:45,362 --> 00:15:47,228
- THIS ISN'T LOOKING GOOD.

288
00:15:47,262 --> 00:15:49,628
- IS THERE NO CHANCE THAT
INUYASHA CAN DEFEAT HIM?

289
00:15:49,662 --> 00:15:53,595
- YEAH. HE STILL DOESN'T KNOW
HOW TO HANDLE TETSUSAIGA.

290
00:15:53,628 --> 00:15:55,862
BESIDES, HE'S UP
AGAINST TOKIJIN,

291
00:15:55,895 --> 00:15:57,828
A DANGEROUS SWORD
IN ANYONE'S HANDS,

292
00:15:57,862 --> 00:16:01,295
AND NOW THAT IT'S BEING
WIELDED BY SESSHOMARU...

293
00:16:01,328 --> 00:16:02,428
[GRUNTING]

294
00:16:02,462 --> 00:16:05,162
- AW, DAMN IT TO HELL.

295
00:16:05,195 --> 00:16:07,495
[GRUNTS]

296
00:16:09,628 --> 00:16:10,995
- JUST AS I THOUGHT.

297
00:16:11,028 --> 00:16:14,728
HIS SCENT IS
BUT THAT OF A HALF-DEMON.

298
00:16:16,928 --> 00:16:21,862
WHEN HE DEFEATED GOSHINKI,
HIS BLOOD CHANGED FOR SURE.

299
00:16:24,162 --> 00:16:25,295
WHAT COULD IT MEAN?

300
00:16:25,328 --> 00:16:29,862
I MUST WITNESS HIS
TRANSFORMATION WITH MY OWN EYES.

301
00:16:35,162 --> 00:16:37,362
- I'LL HAVE TO FINISH HIM
OFF WITH ONE BLOW.

302
00:16:37,395 --> 00:16:39,795
OTHERWISE, I'LL BE KILLED.

303
00:16:39,828 --> 00:16:40,795
[WIND RUSTLES]

304
00:16:40,828 --> 00:16:44,095
- WHAT? HAVE YOU ALTERED
YOUR COMBAT STRATEGY?

305
00:16:44,128 --> 00:16:47,395
USUALLY YOU CHARGE AT ME
BLINDLY WITH GREAT HASTE.

306
00:16:47,428 --> 00:16:50,428
- HUH. WHATEVER YOU SAY.

307
00:16:50,462 --> 00:16:53,362
ARRGH!

308
00:16:55,128 --> 00:16:57,228
[GRUNTING]

309
00:17:07,828 --> 00:17:09,662
[PANTING]

310
00:17:10,128 --> 00:17:13,795
- AHH. TETSUSAIGA HAS
BECOME HEAVIER, I SEE.

311
00:17:13,828 --> 00:17:16,562
- IT'S A LOT HEAVIER,
YOU STUPID JACKASS.

312
00:17:16,595 --> 00:17:19,762
- HMPH. THE SWORD
IS TOO HEAVY FOR YOU.

313
00:17:19,795 --> 00:17:22,262
YOU ARE BETTER OFF WITHOUT IT!

314
00:17:24,528 --> 00:17:26,895
- AAH!

315
00:17:26,928 --> 00:17:29,162
[GRUNTING]

316
00:17:52,663 --> 00:17:53,897
- LOOK AT TETSUSAIGA!

317
00:17:53,930 --> 00:17:55,063
- [GASPING]
INUYASHA!

318
00:17:55,097 --> 00:17:59,230
- HE DOESN'T STAND A CHANCE
AGAINST HIS BROTHER!

319
00:17:59,263 --> 00:18:00,763
- [SIGHS]

320
00:18:00,797 --> 00:18:02,697
[GROWLING]

321
00:18:02,730 --> 00:18:03,763
DAMN IT ALL!

322
00:18:03,797 --> 00:18:07,363
- MASTER INUYASHA, HURRY
AND TAKE HOLD OF TETSUSAIGA!

323
00:18:07,397 --> 00:18:09,230
- MYOGA, YOU AGAIN?

324
00:18:09,263 --> 00:18:11,763
[SIGHS]

325
00:18:15,230 --> 00:18:16,930
DON'T NEED IT.

326
00:18:16,963 --> 00:18:18,897
- STOP! I'M WARNING YOU!

327
00:18:18,930 --> 00:18:20,697
- ARRGH!

328
00:18:20,730 --> 00:18:21,930
- COME BACK, INUYASHA!

329
00:18:21,963 --> 00:18:24,263
- HE'S GOING TO FIGHT HIM
WITH HIS BARE HANDS!

330
00:18:24,297 --> 00:18:26,597
- STOP!
YOU MUSTN'T BE SO RASH!

331
00:18:26,630 --> 00:18:29,263
- I CAN'T USE THAT LUG
OF A SWORD, NOW, CAN I?

332
00:18:29,297 --> 00:18:32,697
- I BEG OF YOU!
- SHUT UP AND STAY BACK!

333
00:18:32,730 --> 00:18:34,130
- AAH!

334
00:18:34,163 --> 00:18:36,430
- ARRGH!

335
00:18:47,463 --> 00:18:49,663
AAH!

336
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:53,230
[GROANING AND SCREAMING]

337
00:19:00,930 --> 00:19:04,263
- HE'S BEEN THROWN
BY THE POWER OF THE SWORD!

338
00:19:08,697 --> 00:19:11,597
[PANTING]

339
00:19:13,497 --> 00:19:16,097
- YOU BASTARD!

340
00:19:25,330 --> 00:19:29,063
- I'VE SEEN ALL THAT I NEEDED.

341
00:19:33,730 --> 00:19:34,597
DIE!

342
00:19:34,630 --> 00:19:37,897
- LOOK OUT, INUYASHA!
HE'S COMING FOR YOU!

343
00:19:47,897 --> 00:19:50,163
THAT SCENT AGAIN!

344
00:19:55,330 --> 00:19:57,497
[GROWLING]

345
00:20:00,897 --> 00:20:02,097
- INUYASHA.

346
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:05,897
OH, NO!
HE'S TRANSFORMED AGAIN!

347
00:20:06,630 --> 00:20:10,097
- YOU PEOPLE TAKE INUYASHA
AND FLEE FROM HERE.

348
00:20:10,130 --> 00:20:11,830
[GASPING]

349
00:20:22,197 --> 00:20:24,363
- TOTOSAI.

350
00:20:24,997 --> 00:20:27,597
- INUYASHA!
- KAGOME, NOW!

351
00:20:27,630 --> 00:20:30,063
- SIT!
- AAH!

352
00:20:49,197 --> 00:20:51,363
[SIZZLING]

353
00:21:03,297 --> 00:21:06,397
- BUT, MY LORD,
WHY DID YOU NOT GO AFTER HIM?

354
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:09,597
HE WAS IN THE PALM
OF YOUR HANDS.

355
00:21:10,897 --> 00:21:13,697
M-MASTER SESSHOMARU?

356
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:19,263
- TO THINK THAT
HE MADE ME, SESSHOMARU,

357
00:21:19,297 --> 00:21:21,997
TREMBLE WITH FEAR
FOR EVEN A MOMENT.

358
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:24,597
[WIND WHISTLING]

359
00:21:27,763 --> 00:21:30,830
INUYASHA, IN THAT INSTANT.

360
00:21:30,863 --> 00:21:33,430
[WIND WHISTLING]

361
00:21:41,430 --> 00:21:43,230
- HE'S STRONG.

362
00:21:43,263 --> 00:21:47,263
HE MIGHT BE ABLE TO KILL NARAKU.

363
00:21:47,297 --> 00:21:49,397
HMM.

364
00:21:50,697 --> 00:21:53,097
[WIND GUSTS]

365
00:22:01,597 --> 00:22:04,530
NARAKU HOLDS MY LIFE
IN HIS HANDS,

366
00:22:04,563 --> 00:22:07,763
BUT I HAVE NO INTENTION
OF REMAINING A SERVANT FOREVER

367
00:22:07,797 --> 00:22:10,030
TO THE LIKES OF HIM.

368
00:22:11,163 --> 00:22:16,830
I AM THE WIND!
ONE DAY, I SHALL BE FREE!

369
00:22:26,905 --> 00:22:29,372
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

370
00:23:56,415 --> 00:23:58,282
- WE MEET JUROMARU,
NARAKU'S FOURTH INCARNATION.

371
00:23:58,315 --> 00:24:02,548
HE IS SO EXPRESSIONLESS,
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE TO TELL
WHERE HE'S LOOKING.

372
00:24:02,582 --> 00:24:04,682
HE MOVES WITH SUCH
LIGHTNING SPEED,

373
00:24:04,715 --> 00:24:06,615
EVEN INUYASHA'S
NO MATCH FOR HIM.

374
00:24:06,648 --> 00:24:10,082
JUROMARU HAS AN OLDER BROTHER
NAMED KAGEROMARU,

375
00:24:10,115 --> 00:24:12,115
AND THEY COME AT US
LIKE A TAG TEAM.

376
00:24:12,148 --> 00:24:15,015
WE'VE GOT MIROKU AND SANGO
ON OUR SIDE, THOUGH,

377
00:24:15,048 --> 00:24:17,282
AND EVEN KOGA COMES TO OUR AID.

378
00:24:17,315 --> 00:24:18,715
NO WAY CAN WE LOSE.

379
00:24:18,748 --> 00:24:22,815
NEXT TIME, "JUROMARU
AND KAGEROMARU."

380
00:24:22,848 --> 00:24:23,848
SEE YOU SOON!

